OL,3,CFather and son jailed after inventing
OL,4,Cstory over crash which injured woman
OL,6,FA father and son have both been jailed
OL,7,Fafter inventing a story over a crash
OL,8,Fwhich left a woman seriously injured
OL,9,Fin Sussex.
OL,11,FLuic Buckley-Barber, 19, was driving
OL,12,Fat high speeds and 'showing off' when
OL,13,Fhe overturned his car into a watery
OL,14,Fditch in Pevensey in April 2023.
OL,16,FA female passenger in the car suffered
OL,17,Fserious injuries.
OL,19,FInstead of calling the emergency
OL,20,Fservices, the then 17-year-old called
OL,21,Fhis father, Jason Barber.
