OL,3,CFather and son jailed after inventing
OL,4,Cstory over crash which injured woman
OL,6,FBarber, 46, drove his son home first
OL,7,Fbefore taking the woman to hospital.
OL,9,FWhile in the car, the woman could hear
OL,10,Fthe father and son inventing a story,
OL,11,Fclaiming the car had been forced off
OL,12,Fthe road to avoid hitting an animal.
OL,14,FAfter the woman was brought into A&E
OL,15,Fat Eastbourne District General
OL,16,FHospital, staff reported the crash to
OL,17,Fpolice.
OL,19,FOfficers later went to Barber's
OL,20,Faddress, but he told officers he
OL,21,Fdidn't know where his son was.
