OL,3,CFather and son jailed after inventing
OL,4,Cstory over crash which injured woman
OL,6,FAt the scene of the crash, beer cans
OL,7,Fwere recovered from around the Ford
OL,8,FEscort, and Buckley-Barber had been
OL,9,Fwith friends at a party earlier in the
OL,10,Fnight.
OL,12,FThe teenager was not found that night,
OL,13,Fand only called police 12 hours later
OL,14,Fwhere he repeated the made-up story.
OL,16,FPhones were seized from the father and
OL,17,Fson, and revealed that Barber sent a
OL,18,Ftext message to a friend, claiming he
OL,19,F"hid" his son from police on the night
OL,20,Fthey were looking for him.
