OL,3,CFather and son jailed after inventing
OL,4,Cstory over crash which injured woman
OL,6,FMobile phone footage also showed
OL,7,FBuckley-Barber's "reckless" driving
OL,8,Fshortly before the crash.
OL,10,FLuic Buckley-Barber, 19, of Maresfield
OL,11,FDrive, Pevensey, pleaded guilty to
OL,12,Fcausing serious injuries by dangerous
OL,13,Fdriving and was sentenced to one year
OL,14,Fand four months in prison, and was
OL,15,Fdisqualified from driving for three
OL,16,Fyears.
OL,18,FJason Barber, 46, of the same address,
OL,19,Fpleaded guilty to perverting the
OL,20,Fcourse of justice and was sentenced to
OL,21,Ftwo years and three months in prison.
